        "subject": "=Task Due Reminder (24 Hours): {{$json.task_title}}\n\n",
        "html": "=<p>Dear {{$json.task_owner_firstname}} {{$json.task_owner_lastname}},</p>\n\n<p>This is a reminder that the task <b>{{$json.task_title}}</b> is due within the next <b>24 hours</b>.</p>\n\n<p>Task Schedule:<br>\n* Task Title: {{$json.task_title}}<br>\n* Due Date: {{$json.task_due_date}}<br>\n* Current Status: {{$json.task_status}}</p>\n\n<p>Please prioritize completion or update the task with revised timelines if required.</p>\n\n<p>Regards,<br>\nTask Management System</p>",
